          "title": "Broadcast to the mempool",
          "plain": "The signed request is sent out to the blockchain's waiting room, where it lines up to be processed.",
          "detail": "eth_sendRawTransaction pushes the tx to an RPC node and into the public mempool, or a private relay like Flashbots Protect to dodge MEV. Validators and sequencers now see it as pending.",
